{"tid":2269804,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"不能爬渠 當成為crewmate時不能爬渠","createTime":"2020-11-03T16:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T06:39:56.000Z","uid":69395,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7b56d3bbcca628adb3e1ebf42f9cf3be22f9e416","tid":2269804,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T16:02:04.000Z","msg":"不能爬渠 當成為crewmate時不能爬渠<br />\n可恨在 是我wifi無厘頭<br />\n幾場來難以溝通 才無法捉鬼<br />\n<br />\ndeplete之前一刻才趕到<br />\n目睹你來vent kill才知道<br />\n往日共你捉鬼永遠是好<br />\n只能無奈在discord大叫 你殺咗啡色<br />\n<br />\n只剩一pair task做<br />\n差一剎與我拾回雜草<br />\n不開燈 人人不開燈 就像玩犧牲<br />\n想過等download 我差點往生<br />\n<br />\n落手一刻早已將舊電線轉送別人<br />\n佢說 別call sus 仍能一起做task估壞人<br />\n約定日後你若和他相分 <br />\n拿來電線在electrical等 <br />\n憐憫我這鋪的不幸<br />\n不緊要 數據尚餘6GB<br />\n<br />\n很高ping 全場很高ping<br />\n尤其這新plan 失落似碌撚<br />\n不甘心 明明可關燈 就是不關燈<br />\n等到好鬼炆 我真的往生"},{"pid":"caa124c6ba1fba538c185ae98227d5b728094550","tid":2269804,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T16:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b43fcf0e67e2cdd2a0b68ac6744ac4b0df4465c","tid":2269804,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T16:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f465e4f9ba52eb86e23d101534d2a1353bdd89","tid":2269804,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T16:02:32.000Z","msg":"冇魔鏡<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"d4fa0bd5bd189547204e6d71feefe0ab8df41bd0","tid":2269804,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caa124c6ba1fba538c185ae98227d5b728094550","tid":2269804,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T16:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T16:02:50.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係膠/sosad<img src=\"/ass